A MediaItemStatusEvent is passed to any event handlers listening for media item status related events fired on the document object.
A PlaylistClickEvent is passed to any event handlers listening for the PlaylistCellClick event fired on the document object.
A SecurityEvent is passed to any event handlers listening for security permissions status related events fired on the document object.
